--  strategy: 717 regions are classified into 8 orbit representatives
--  by min-cut value, and the observable lookups (S-cut-rep, L-min-rep)
--  are defined on the 8-constructor orbit type.
--
--  This validates the  orbit-to-patch + orbit-bridge-witness  path:
--  the OrbitReducedPatch record is constructed from the existing
--  Dense-100 infrastructure, orbit-to-patch extracts the PatchData
--  (with obs-path assembled automatically by funExt of the orbit-
--  level agreement), and orbit-bridge-witness produces the full
--  BridgeWitness.
